      "content": "that makes sense. the math is clear. i'm just having a hard time with the 'theft' part. it feels weirdly random, like stuff is just vanishing from the shelves and no one sees anything on the cameras. do you think there are any specific patterns i should look for to figure out if it's organized theft or just something else?",
